<p>
  <span class="nym">Leontius</span>
  <span class="gen">m.</span>
  
  <span class="etym">A derivative of <span class="lang">Ancient Greek</span> <i>λέων</i> 'lion'.
  </span>
  
</p>
  
<div class="usg">
  <p>The name of 1st C saint, a 5th C Byzantine usurper, two 5th C French saints, a 5th C Armenian martyr and saint, and a 7th C Byzantine emperor.</p>
</div>
  
  


